00170 int
00171 cuddZddSymmCheck(
00172   DdManager * table,
00173   int  x,
00174   int  y)
00175 {
00176     int         i;
00177     DdNode      *f, *f0, *f1, *f01, *f00, *f11, *f10;
00178     int         yindex;
00179     int         xsymmy = 1;
00180     int         xsymmyp = 1;
00181     int         arccount = 0;
00182     int         TotalRefCount = 0;
00183     int         symm_found;
00184 
00185     empty = table->zero;
00186 
00187     yindex = table->invpermZ[y];
00188     for (i = table->subtableZ[x].slots - 1; i >= 0; i--) {
00189         f = table->subtableZ[x].nodelist[i];
00190         while (f != NULL) {
00191             /* Find f1, f0, f11, f10, f01, f00 */
00192             f1 = cuddT(f);
00193             f0 = cuddE(f);
00194             if ((int) f1->index == yindex) {
00195                 f11 = cuddT(f1);
00196                 f10 = cuddE(f1);
00197                 if (f10 != empty)
00198                     arccount++;
00199             } else {
00200                 if ((int) f0->index != yindex) {
00201                     return(0); /* f bypasses layer y */
00202                 }
00203                 f11 = empty;
00204                 f10 = f1;
00205             }
00206             if ((int) f0->index == yindex) {
00207                 f01 = cuddT(f0);
00208                 f00 = cuddE(f0);
00209                 if (f00 != empty)
00210                     arccount++;
00211             } else {
00212                 f01 = empty;
00213                 f00 = f0;
00214             }
00215             if (f01 != f10)
00216                 xsymmy = 0;
00217             if (f11 != f00)
00218                 xsymmyp = 0;
00219             if ((xsymmy == 0) && (xsymmyp == 0))
00220                 return(0);
00221 
00222             f = f->next;
00223         } /* for each element of the collision list */
00224     } /* for each slot of the subtable */
00225 
00226     /* Calculate the total reference counts of y
00227     ** whose else arc is not empty.
00228     */
00229     for (i = table->subtableZ[y].slots - 1; i >= 0; i--) {
00230         f = table->subtableZ[y].nodelist[i];
00231         while (f != NIL(DdNode)) {
00232             if (cuddE(f) != empty)
00233                 TotalRefCount += f->ref;
00234             f = f->next;
00235         }
00236     }
00237 
00238     symm_found = (arccount == TotalRefCount);
00239 #if defined(DD_DEBUG) && defined(DD_VERBOSE)
00240     if (symm_found) {
00241         int xindex = table->invpermZ[x];
00242         (void) fprintf(stdout,"Found symmetry! x =%d\ty = %d\tPos(%d,%d)\n",
00243                        xindex,yindex,x,y);
00244     }
00245 #endif
00246 
00247     return(symm_found);
00248 
00249 } /* end cuddZddSymmCheck */

00294     /* Find order in which to sift variables. */
00295     var = NULL;
00296     zdd_entry = ALLOC(int, nvars);

00298         table->errorCode = CUDD_MEMORY_OUT;
00299         goto cuddZddSymmSiftingOutOfMem;

00301     var = ALLOC(int, nvars);
00302     if (var == NULL) {

00304         goto cuddZddSymmSiftingOutOfMem;

00306 
00307     for (i = 0; i < nvars; i++) {
00308         x = table->permZ[i];
00309         zdd_entry[i] = table->subtableZ[x].keys;
00310         var[i] = i;
00311     }
00312

00314 
00315     /* Initialize the symmetry of each subtable to itself. */
00316     for (i = lower; i <= upper; i++)
00317         table->subtableZ[i].next = i;
00318

00320     for (i = 0; i < iteration; i++) {
00321         if (zddTotalNumberSwapping >= table->siftMaxSwap)
00322             break;
00323         x = table->permZ[var[i]];
00324 #ifdef DD_STATS
00325         previousSize = table->keysZ;
00326 #endif
00327         if (x < lower || x > upper) continue;
00328         if (table->subtableZ[x].next == (unsigned) x) {
00329             result = cuddZddSymmSiftingAux(table, x, lower, upper);
00330             if (!result)
00331                 goto cuddZddSymmSiftingOutOfMem;
00332 #ifdef DD_STATS
00333             if (table->keysZ < (unsigned) previousSize) {
00334                 (void) fprintf(stdout,"-");
00335             } else if (table->keysZ > (unsigned) previousSize) {
00336                 (void) fprintf(stdout,"+");
00337 #ifdef DD_VERBOSE
00338                 (void) fprintf(stdout,"\nSize increased from %d to %d while sifting variable %d\n", previousSize, table->keysZ, var[i]);
00339 #endif
00340             } else {
00341                 (void) fprintf(stdout,"=");
00342             }
00343             fflush(stdout);
00344 #endif
00345         }
00346     }
00347 
00348     FREE(var);
00349     FREE(zdd_entry);
00350 
00351     cuddZddSymmSummary(table, lower, upper, &symvars, &symgroups);
00352 
00353 #ifdef DD_STATS
00354     (void) fprintf(stdout,"\n#:S_SIFTING %8d: symmetric variables\n",symvars);
00355     (void) fprintf(stdout,"#:G_SIFTING %8d: symmetric groups\n",symgroups);

00358     return(1+symvars);
00359 
00360 cuddZddSymmSiftingOutOfMem:
00361 
00362     if (zdd_entry != NULL)
00363         FREE(zdd_entry);

00420     var = NULL;
00421     zdd_entry = ALLOC(int, nvars);

00423         table->errorCode = CUDD_MEMORY_OUT;
00424         goto cuddZddSymmSiftingConvOutOfMem;
00425     }
00426     var = ALLOC(int, nvars);
00427     if (var == NULL) {
00428         table->errorCode = CUDD_MEMORY_OUT;
00429         goto cuddZddSymmSiftingConvOutOfMem;

00431 
00432     for (i = 0; i < nvars; i++) {
00433         x = table->permZ[i];
00434         zdd_entry[i] = table->subtableZ[x].keys;
00435         var[i] = i;
00436     }
00437 
00438     qsort((void *)var, nvars, sizeof(int), (int (*)(const void *, const void *))cuddZddUniqueCompare);
00439 
00440     /* Initialize the symmetry of each subtable to itself
00441     ** for first pass of converging symmetric sifting.
00442     */
00443     for (i = lower; i <= upper; i++)
00444         table->subtableZ[i].next = i;
00445 
00446     iteration = ddMin(table->siftMaxVar, table->sizeZ);
00447     for (i = 0; i < iteration; i++) {
00448         if (zddTotalNumberSwapping >= table->siftMaxSwap)
00449             break;
00450         x = table->permZ[var[i]];
00451         if (x < lower || x > upper) continue;
00452         /* Only sift if not in symmetry group already. */
00453         if (table->subtableZ[x].next == (unsigned) x) {
00454 #ifdef DD_STATS
00455             previousSize = table->keysZ;
00456 #endif
00457             result = cuddZddSymmSiftingAux(table, x, lower, upper);
00458             if (!result)

00467 #endif
00468             } else {
00469                 (void) fprintf(stdout,"=");
00470             }
00471             fflush(stdout);
00472 #endif
00473         }
00474     }
00475 
00476     /* Sifting now until convergence. */
00477     while ((unsigned) initialSize > table->keysZ) {
00478         initialSize = table->keysZ;
00479 #ifdef DD_STATS
00480         (void) fprintf(stdout,"\n");
00481 #endif
00482         /* Here we consider only one representative for each symmetry class. */
00483         for (x = lower, classes = 0; x <= upper; x++, classes++) {
00484             while ((unsigned) x < table->subtableZ[x].next)
00485                 x = table->subtableZ[x].next;
00486             /* Here x is the largest index in a group.
00487             ** Groups consists of adjacent variables.
00488             ** Hence, the next increment of x will move it to a new group.
00489             */
00490             i = table->invpermZ[x];
00491             zdd_entry[i] = table->subtableZ[x].keys;
00492             var[classes] = i;
00493         }
00494 
00495         qsort((void *)var,classes,sizeof(int),(int (*)(const void *, const void *))cuddZddUniqueCompare);
00496 
00497         /* Now sift. */
00498         iteration = ddMin(table->siftMaxVar, nvars);
00499         for (i = 0; i < iteration; i++) {
00500             if (zddTotalNumberSwapping >= table->siftMaxSwap)
00501                 break;
00502             x = table->permZ[var[i]];
00503             if ((unsigned) x >= table->subtableZ[x].next) {
00504 #ifdef DD_STATS
00505                 previousSize = table->keysZ;
00506 #endif
00507                 result = cuddZddSymmSiftingConvAux(table, x, lower, upper);
00508                 if (!result)

00510 #ifdef DD_STATS
00511                 if (table->keysZ < (unsigned) previousSize) {
00512                     (void) fprintf(stdout,"-");
00513                 } else if (table->keysZ > (unsigned) previousSize) {
00514                     (void) fprintf(stdout,"+");
00515 #ifdef DD_VERBOSE
00516                 (void) fprintf(stdout,"\nSize increased from %d to %d while sifting variable %d\n", previousSize, table->keysZ, var[i]);
00517 #endif
00518                 } else {
00519                     (void) fprintf(stdout,"=");
00520                 }
00521                 fflush(stdout);
00522 #endif
00523             }
00524         } /* for */
00525     }
00526 
00527     cuddZddSymmSummary(table, lower, upper, &symvars, &symgroups);
00528 
00529 #ifdef DD_STATS
00530     (void) fprintf(stdout,"\n#:S_SIFTING %8d: symmetric variables\n",symvars);
00531     (void) fprintf(stdout,"#:G_SIFTING %8d: symmetric groups\n",symgroups);
00532 #endif
00533 
00534     FREE(var);
00535     FREE(zdd_entry);
00536 
00537     return(1+symvars);
00538 
00539 cuddZddSymmSiftingConvOutOfMem:
00540 
00541     if (zdd_entry != NULL)
00542         FREE(zdd_entry);

00571 static int
00572 cuddZddSymmSiftingAux(
00573   DdManager * table,
00574   int  x,
00575   int  x_low,
00576   int  x_high)
00577 {
00578     Move *move;
00579     Move *move_up;      /* list of up move */
00580     Move *move_down;    /* list of down move */
00581     int  initial_size;
00582     int  result;
00583     int  i;
00584     int  topbot;        /* index to either top or bottom of symmetry group */
00585     int  init_group_size, final_group_size;
00586 
00587     initial_size = table->keysZ;
00588 
00589     move_down = NULL;
00590     move_up = NULL;
00591 
00592     /* Look for consecutive symmetries above x. */
00593     for (i = x; i > x_low; i--) {
00594         if (!cuddZddSymmCheck(table, i - 1, i))
00595             break;
00596         /* find top of i-1's symmetry */
00597         topbot = table->subtableZ[i - 1].next;
00598         table->subtableZ[i - 1].next = i;
00599         table->subtableZ[x].next = topbot;
00600         /* x is bottom of group so its symmetry is top of i-1's
00601            group */
00602         i = topbot + 1; /* add 1 for i--, new i is top of symm group */
00603     }
00604     /* Look for consecutive symmetries below x. */
00605     for (i = x; i < x_high; i++) {
00606         if (!cuddZddSymmCheck(table, i, i + 1))
00607             break;
00608         /* find bottom of i+1's symm group */
00609         topbot = i + 1;
00610         while ((unsigned) topbot < table->subtableZ[topbot].next)
00611             topbot = table->subtableZ[topbot].next;
00612 
00613         table->subtableZ[topbot].next = table->subtableZ[i].next;
00614         table->subtableZ[i].next = i + 1;
00615         i = topbot - 1; /* add 1 for i++,
00616                            new i is bottom of symm group */
00617     }
00618 
00619     /* Now x maybe in the middle of a symmetry group. */
00620     if (x == x_low) { /* Sift down */
00621         /* Find bottom of x's symm group */
00622         while ((unsigned) x < table->subtableZ[x].next)
00623             x = table->subtableZ[x].next;
00624 
00625         i = table->subtableZ[x].next;
00626         init_group_size = x - i + 1;
00627 
00628         move_down = cuddZddSymmSifting_down(table, x, x_high,
00629             initial_size);
00630         /* after that point x --> x_high, unless early term */
00631         if (move_down == ZDD_MV_OOM)
00632             goto cuddZddSymmSiftingAuxOutOfMem;
00633 
00634         if (move_down == NULL ||
00635             table->subtableZ[move_down->y].next != move_down->y) {
00636             /* symmetry detected may have to make another complete
00637                pass */
00638             if (move_down != NULL)
00639                 x = move_down->y;
00640             else
00641                 x = table->subtableZ[x].next;
00642             i = x;
00643             while ((unsigned) i < table->subtableZ[i].next) {
00644                 i = table->subtableZ[i].next;
00645             }
00646             final_group_size = i - x + 1;
00647 
00648             if (init_group_size == final_group_size) {
00649                 /* No new symmetry groups detected,
00650                    return to best position */
00651                 result = cuddZddSymmSiftingBackward(table,
00652                     move_down, initial_size);
00653             }
00654             else {
00655                 initial_size = table->keysZ;
00656                 move_up = cuddZddSymmSifting_up(table, x, x_low,
00657                     initial_size);
00658                 result = cuddZddSymmSiftingBackward(table, move_up,
00659                     initial_size);
00660             }
00661         }
00662         else {
00663             result = cuddZddSymmSiftingBackward(table, move_down,
00664                 initial_size);
00665             /* move backward and stop at best position */
00666         }
00667         if (!result)
00668             goto cuddZddSymmSiftingAuxOutOfMem;
00669     }
00670     else if (x == x_high) { /* Sift up */
00671         /* Find top of x's symm group */
00672         while ((unsigned) x < table->subtableZ[x].next)
00673             x = table->subtableZ[x].next;
00674         x = table->subtableZ[x].next;
00675 
00676         i = x;
00677         while ((unsigned) i < table->subtableZ[i].next) {
00678             i = table->subtableZ[i].next;
00679         }
00680         init_group_size = i - x + 1;
00681 
00682         move_up = cuddZddSymmSifting_up(table, x, x_low, initial_size);
00683         /* after that point x --> x_low, unless early term */
00684         if (move_up == ZDD_MV_OOM)
00685             goto cuddZddSymmSiftingAuxOutOfMem;
00686 
00687         if (move_up == NULL ||
00688             table->subtableZ[move_up->x].next != move_up->x) {
00689             /* symmetry detected may have to make another complete
00690                 pass */
00691             if (move_up != NULL)
00692                 x = move_up->x;
00693             else {
00694                 while ((unsigned) x < table->subtableZ[x].next)
00695                     x = table->subtableZ[x].next;
00696             }
00697             i = table->subtableZ[x].next;
00698             final_group_size = x - i + 1;
00699 
00700             if (init_group_size == final_group_size) {
00701                 /* No new symmetry groups detected,
00702                    return to best position */
00703                 result = cuddZddSymmSiftingBackward(table, move_up,
00704                     initial_size);
00705             }
00706             else {
00707                 initial_size = table->keysZ;
00708                 move_down = cuddZddSymmSifting_down(table, x, x_high,
00709                     initial_size);
00710                 result = cuddZddSymmSiftingBackward(table, move_down,
00711                     initial_size);
00712             }
00713         }
00714         else {
00715             result = cuddZddSymmSiftingBackward(table, move_up,
00716                 initial_size);
00717             /* move backward and stop at best position */
00718         }
00719         if (!result)
00720             goto cuddZddSymmSiftingAuxOutOfMem;
00721     }
00722     else if ((x - x_low) > (x_high - x)) { /* must go down first:
00723                                                 shorter */
00724         /* Find bottom of x's symm group */
00725         while ((unsigned) x < table->subtableZ[x].next)
00726             x = table->subtableZ[x].next;
00727 
00728         move_down = cuddZddSymmSifting_down(table, x, x_high,
00729             initial_size);
00730         /* after that point x --> x_high, unless early term */
00731         if (move_down == ZDD_MV_OOM)
00732             goto cuddZddSymmSiftingAuxOutOfMem;
00733 
00734         if (move_down != NULL) {
00735             x = move_down->y;
00736         }
00737         else {
00738             x = table->subtableZ[x].next;
00739         }
00740         i = x;
00741         while ((unsigned) i < table->subtableZ[i].next) {
00742             i = table->subtableZ[i].next;
00743         }
00744         init_group_size = i - x + 1;
00745 
00746         move_up = cuddZddSymmSifting_up(table, x, x_low, initial_size);
00747         if (move_up == ZDD_MV_OOM)
00748             goto cuddZddSymmSiftingAuxOutOfMem;
00749 
00750         if (move_up == NULL ||
00751             table->subtableZ[move_up->x].next != move_up->x) {
00752             /* symmetry detected may have to make another complete
00753                pass */
00754             if (move_up != NULL) {
00755                 x = move_up->x;
00756             }
00757             else {
00758                 while ((unsigned) x < table->subtableZ[x].next)
00759                     x = table->subtableZ[x].next;
00760             }
00761             i = table->subtableZ[x].next;
00762             final_group_size = x - i + 1;
00763 
00764             if (init_group_size == final_group_size) {
00765                 /* No new symmetry groups detected,
00766                    return to best position */
00767                 result = cuddZddSymmSiftingBackward(table, move_up,
00768                     initial_size);
00769             }
00770             else {
00771                 while (move_down != NULL) {
00772                     move = move_down->next;
00773                     cuddDeallocNode(table, (DdNode *)move_down);
00774                     move_down = move;
00775                 }
00776                 initial_size = table->keysZ;
00777                 move_down = cuddZddSymmSifting_down(table, x, x_high,
00778                     initial_size);
00779                 result = cuddZddSymmSiftingBackward(table, move_down,
00780                     initial_size);
00781             }
00782         }
00783         else {
00784             result = cuddZddSymmSiftingBackward(table, move_up,
00785                 initial_size);
00786             /* move backward and stop at best position */
00787         }
00788         if (!result)
00789             goto cuddZddSymmSiftingAuxOutOfMem;
00790     }
00791     else { /* moving up first:shorter */
00792         /* Find top of x's symmetry group */
00793         while ((unsigned) x < table->subtableZ[x].next)
00794             x = table->subtableZ[x].next;
00795         x = table->subtableZ[x].next;
00796 
00797         move_up = cuddZddSymmSifting_up(table, x, x_low, initial_size);
00798         /* after that point x --> x_high, unless early term */
00799         if (move_up == ZDD_MV_OOM)
00800             goto cuddZddSymmSiftingAuxOutOfMem;
00801 
00802         if (move_up != NULL) {
00803             x = move_up->x;
00804         }
00805         else {
00806             while ((unsigned) x < table->subtableZ[x].next)
00807                 x = table->subtableZ[x].next;
00808         }
00809         i = table->subtableZ[x].next;
00810         init_group_size = x - i + 1;
00811 
00812         move_down = cuddZddSymmSifting_down(table, x, x_high,
00813             initial_size);
00814         if (move_down == ZDD_MV_OOM)
00815             goto cuddZddSymmSiftingAuxOutOfMem;
00816 
00817         if (move_down == NULL ||
00818             table->subtableZ[move_down->y].next != move_down->y) {
00819             /* symmetry detected may have to make another complete
00820                pass */
00821             if (move_down != NULL) {
00822                 x = move_down->y;
00823             }
00824             else {
00825                 x = table->subtableZ[x].next;
00826             }
00827             i = x;
00828             while ((unsigned) i < table->subtableZ[i].next) {
00829                 i = table->subtableZ[i].next;
00830             }
00831             final_group_size = i - x + 1;
00832 
00833             if (init_group_size == final_group_size) {
00834                 /* No new symmetries detected,
00835                    go back to best position */
00836                 result = cuddZddSymmSiftingBackward(table, move_down,
00837                     initial_size);
00838             }
00839             else {
00840                 while (move_up != NULL) {
00841                     move = move_up->next;
00842                     cuddDeallocNode(table, (DdNode *)move_up);
00843                     move_up = move;
00844                 }
00845                 initial_size = table->keysZ;
00846                 move_up = cuddZddSymmSifting_up(table, x, x_low,
00847                     initial_size);
00848                 result = cuddZddSymmSiftingBackward(table, move_up,
00849                     initial_size);
00850             }
00851         }
00852         else {
00853             result = cuddZddSymmSiftingBackward(table, move_down,
00854                 initial_size);
00855             /* move backward and stop at best position */
00856         }
00857         if (!result)
00858             goto cuddZddSymmSiftingAuxOutOfMem;
00859     }
00860 
00861     while (move_down != NULL) {
00862         move = move_down->next;
00863         cuddDeallocNode(table, (DdNode *)move_down);
00864         move_down = move;
00865     }
00866     while (move_up != NULL) {
00867         move = move_up->next;
00868         cuddDeallocNode(table, (DdNode *)move_up);
00869         move_up = move;
00870     }
00871 
00872     return(1);
00873 
00874 cuddZddSymmSiftingAuxOutOfMem:
00875     while (move_down != NULL) {
00876         move = move_down->next;
00877         cuddDeallocNode(table, (DdNode *)move_down);
00878         move_down = move;
00879     }
00880     while (move_up != NULL) {
00881         move = move_up->next;
00882         cuddDeallocNode(table, (DdNode *)move_up);
00883         move_up = move;
00884     }
00885 
00886     return(0);
00887 
00888 } /* end of cuddZddSymmSiftingAux */

01194 
01212 static Move *
01213 cuddZddSymmSifting_up(
01214   DdManager * table,
01215   int  x,
01216   int  x_low,
01217   int  initial_size)
01218 {
01219     Move        *moves;
01220     Move        *move;
01221     int         y;
01222     int         size;
01223     int         limit_size = initial_size;
01224     int         i, gytop;
01225 
01226     moves = NULL;
01227     y = cuddZddNextLow(table, x);
01228     while (y >= x_low) {
01229         gytop = table->subtableZ[y].next;
01230         if (cuddZddSymmCheck(table, y, x)) {
01231             /* Symmetry found, attach symm groups */
01232             table->subtableZ[y].next = x;
01233             i = table->subtableZ[x].next;
01234             while (table->subtableZ[i].next != (unsigned) x)
01235                 i = table->subtableZ[i].next;
01236             table->subtableZ[i].next = gytop;
01237         }
01238         else if ((table->subtableZ[x].next == (unsigned) x) &&
01239             (table->subtableZ[y].next == (unsigned) y)) {
01240             /* x and y have self symmetry */
01241             size = cuddZddSwapInPlace(table, y, x);
01242             if (size == 0)
01243                 goto cuddZddSymmSifting_upOutOfMem;
01244             move = (Move *)cuddDynamicAllocNode(table);
01245             if (move == NULL)
01246                 goto cuddZddSymmSifting_upOutOfMem;
01247             move->x = y;
01248             move->y = x;
01249             move->size = size;
01250             move->next = moves;
01251             moves = move;
01252             if ((double)size >
01253                 (double)limit_size * table->maxGrowth)
01254                 return(moves);
01255             if (size < limit_size)
01256                 limit_size = size;
01257         }
01258         else { /* Group move */
01259             size = zdd_group_move(table, y, x, &moves);
01260             if ((double)size >
01261                 (double)limit_size * table->maxGrowth)
01262                 return(moves);
01263             if (size < limit_size)
01264                 limit_size = size;
01265         }
01266         x = gytop;
01267         y = cuddZddNextLow(table, x);
01268     }
01269 
01270     return(moves);
01271 
01272 cuddZddSymmSifting_upOutOfMem:
01273     while (moves != NULL) {
01274         move = moves->next;
01275         cuddDeallocNode(table, (DdNode *)moves);
01276         moves = move;
01277     }
01278     return(ZDD_MV_OOM);
01279 
01280 } /* end of cuddZddSymmSifting_up */

01300 static Move *
01301 cuddZddSymmSifting_down(
01302   DdManager * table,
01303   int  x,
01304   int  x_high,
01305   int  initial_size)
01306 {
01307     Move        *moves;
01308     Move        *move;
01309     int         y;
01310     int         size;
01311     int         limit_size = initial_size;
01312     int         i, gxtop, gybot;
01313 
01314     moves = NULL;
01315     y = cuddZddNextHigh(table, x);
01316     while (y <= x_high) {
01317         gybot = table->subtableZ[y].next;
01318         while (table->subtableZ[gybot].next != (unsigned) y)
01319             gybot = table->subtableZ[gybot].next;
01320         if (cuddZddSymmCheck(table, x, y)) {
01321             /* Symmetry found, attach symm groups */
01322             gxtop = table->subtableZ[x].next;
01323             table->subtableZ[x].next = y;
01324             i = table->subtableZ[y].next;
01325             while (table->subtableZ[i].next != (unsigned) y)
01326                 i = table->subtableZ[i].next;
01327             table->subtableZ[i].next = gxtop;
01328         }
01329         else if ((table->subtableZ[x].next == (unsigned) x) &&
01330             (table->subtableZ[y].next == (unsigned) y)) {
01331             /* x and y have self symmetry */
01332             size = cuddZddSwapInPlace(table, x, y);
01333             if (size == 0)
01334                 goto cuddZddSymmSifting_downOutOfMem;
01335             move = (Move *)cuddDynamicAllocNode(table);
01336             if (move == NULL)
01337                 goto cuddZddSymmSifting_downOutOfMem;
01338             move->x = x;
01339             move->y = y;
01340             move->size = size;
01341             move->next = moves;
01342             moves = move;
01343             if ((double)size >
01344                 (double)limit_size * table->maxGrowth)
01345                 return(moves);
01346             if (size < limit_size)
01347                 limit_size = size;
01348             x = y;
01349             y = cuddZddNextHigh(table, x);
01350         }
01351         else { /* Group move */
01352             size = zdd_group_move(table, x, y, &moves);
01353             if ((double)size >
01354                 (double)limit_size * table->maxGrowth)
01355                 return(moves);
01356             if (size < limit_size)
01357                 limit_size = size;
01358         }
01359         x = gybot;
01360         y = cuddZddNextHigh(table, x);
01361     }
01362 
01363     return(moves);
01364 
01365 cuddZddSymmSifting_downOutOfMem:
01366     while (moves != NULL) {
01367         move = moves->next;
01368         cuddDeallocNode(table, (DdNode *)moves);
01369         moves = move;
01370     }
01371     return(ZDD_MV_OOM);
01372 
01373 } /* end of cuddZddSymmSifting_down */

01375 
01391 static int
01392 cuddZddSymmSiftingBackward(
01393   DdManager * table,
01394   Move * moves,
01395   int  size)
01396 {
01397     int         i;
01398     int         i_best;
01399     Move        *move;
01400     int         res;
01401 
01402     i_best = -1;
01403     for (move = moves, i = 0; move != NULL; move = move->next, i++) {
01404         if (move->size < size) {
01405             i_best = i;
01406             size = move->size;
01407         }
01408     }
01409 
01410     for (move = moves, i = 0; move != NULL; move = move->next, i++) {
01411         if (i == i_best) break;
01412         if ((table->subtableZ[move->x].next == move->x) &&
01413             (table->subtableZ[move->y].next == move->y)) {
01414             res = cuddZddSwapInPlace(table, move->x, move->y);
01415             if (!res) return(0);
01416         }
01417         else { /* Group move necessary */
01418             res = zdd_group_move_backward(table, move->x, move->y);
01419         }
01420         if (i_best == -1 && res == size)
01421             break;
01422     }
01423 
01424     return(1);
01425 
01426 } /* end of cuddZddSymmSiftingBackward */

01428 
01443 static int
01444 zdd_group_move(
01445   DdManager * table,
01446   int  x,
01447   int  y,
01448   Move ** moves)
01449 {
01450     Move        *move;
01451     int         size;
01452     int         i, temp, gxtop, gxbot, gytop, gybot, yprev;
01453     int         swapx = 0, swapy = 0;
01454 
01455 #ifdef DD_DEBUG
01456     assert(x < y);      /* we assume that x < y */
01457 #endif
01458     /* Find top and bottom for the two groups. */
01459     gxtop = table->subtableZ[x].next;
01460     gytop = y;
01461     gxbot = x;
01462     gybot = table->subtableZ[y].next;
01463     while (table->subtableZ[gybot].next != (unsigned) y)
01464         gybot = table->subtableZ[gybot].next;
01465     yprev = gybot;
01466 
01467     while (x <= y) {
01468         while (y > gxtop) {
01469             /* Set correct symmetries. */
01470             temp = table->subtableZ[x].next;
01471             if (temp == x)
01472                 temp = y;
01473             i = gxtop;
01474             for (;;) {
01475                 if (table->subtableZ[i].next == (unsigned) x) {
01476                     table->subtableZ[i].next = y;
01477                     break;
01478                 } else {
01479                     i = table->subtableZ[i].next;
01480                 }
01481             }
01482             if (table->subtableZ[y].next != (unsigned) y) {
01483                 table->subtableZ[x].next = table->subtableZ[y].next;
01484             } else {
01485                 table->subtableZ[x].next = x;
01486             }
01487 
01488             if (yprev != y) {
01489                 table->subtableZ[yprev].next = x;
01490             } else {
01491                 yprev = x;
01492             }
01493             table->subtableZ[y].next = temp;
01494 
01495             size = cuddZddSwapInPlace(table, x, y);
01496             if (size == 0)
01497                 goto zdd_group_moveOutOfMem;
01498             swapx = x;
01499             swapy = y;
01500             y = x;
01501             x--;
01502         } /* while y > gxtop */
01503 
01504         /* Trying to find the next y. */
01505         if (table->subtableZ[y].next <= (unsigned) y) {
01506             gybot = y;
01507         } else {
01508             y = table->subtableZ[y].next;
01509         }
01510 
01511         yprev = gxtop;
01512         gxtop++;
01513         gxbot++;
01514         x = gxbot;
01515     } /* while x <= y, end of group movement */
01516     move = (Move *)cuddDynamicAllocNode(table);
01517     if (move == NULL)
01518         goto zdd_group_moveOutOfMem;
01519     move->x = swapx;
01520     move->y = swapy;
01521     move->size = table->keysZ;
01522     move->next = *moves;
01523     *moves = move;
01524 
01525     return(table->keysZ);
01526 
01527 zdd_group_moveOutOfMem:
01528     while (*moves != NULL) {
01529         move = (*moves)->next;
01530         cuddDeallocNode(table, (DdNode *)(*moves));
01531         *moves = move;
01532     }
01533     return(0);
01534 
01535 } /* end of zdd_group_move */

01551 static int
01552 zdd_group_move_backward(
01553   DdManager * table,
01554   int  x,
01555   int  y)
01556 {
01557     int        size = 0;
01558     int        i, temp, gxtop, gxbot, gytop, gybot, yprev;
01559 
01560 #ifdef DD_DEBUG
01561     assert(x < y);      /* we assume that x < y */
01562 #endif
01563     /* Find top and bottom of the two groups. */
01564     gxtop = table->subtableZ[x].next;
01565     gytop = y;
01566     gxbot = x;
01567     gybot = table->subtableZ[y].next;
01568     while (table->subtableZ[gybot].next != (unsigned) y)
01569         gybot = table->subtableZ[gybot].next;
01570     yprev = gybot;
01571 
01572     while (x <= y) {
01573         while (y > gxtop) {
01574             /* Set correct symmetries. */
01575             temp = table->subtableZ[x].next;
01576             if (temp == x)
01577                 temp = y;
01578             i = gxtop;
01579             for (;;) {
01580                 if (table->subtableZ[i].next == (unsigned) x) {
01581                     table->subtableZ[i].next = y;
01582                     break;
01583                 } else {
01584                     i = table->subtableZ[i].next;
01585                 }
01586             }
01587             if (table->subtableZ[y].next != (unsigned) y) {
01588                 table->subtableZ[x].next = table->subtableZ[y].next;
01589             } else {
01590                 table->subtableZ[x].next = x;
01591             }
01592 
01593             if (yprev != y) {
01594                 table->subtableZ[yprev].next = x;
01595             } else {
01596                 yprev = x;
01597             }
01598             table->subtableZ[y].next = temp;
01599 
01600             size = cuddZddSwapInPlace(table, x, y);
01601             if (size == 0)
01602                 return(0);
01603             y = x;
01604             x--;
01605         } /* while y > gxtop */
01606 
01607         /* Trying to find the next y. */
01608         if (table->subtableZ[y].next <= (unsigned) y) {
01609             gybot = y;
01610         } else {
01611             y = table->subtableZ[y].next;
01612         }
01613 
01614         yprev = gxtop;
01615         gxtop++;
01616         gxbot++;
01617         x = gxbot;
01618     } /* while x <= y, end of group movement backward */
01619 
01620     return(size);
01621 
01622 } /* end of zdd_group_move_backward */

01635 static void
01636 cuddZddSymmSummary(
01637   DdManager * table,
01638   int  lower,
01639   int  upper,
01640   int * symvars,
01641   int * symgroups)
01642 {
01643     int i,x,gbot;
01644     int TotalSymm = 0;
01645     int TotalSymmGroups = 0;
01646 
01647     for (i = lower; i <= upper; i++) {
01648         if (table->subtableZ[i].next != (unsigned) i) {
01649             TotalSymmGroups++;
01650             x = i;
01651             do {
01652                 TotalSymm++;
01653                 gbot = x;
01654                 x = table->subtableZ[x].next;
01655             } while (x != i);
01656 #ifdef DD_DEBUG
01657             assert(table->subtableZ[gbot].next == (unsigned) i);
01658 #endif
01659             i = gbot;
01660         }
01661     }
01662     *symvars = TotalSymm;
01663     *symgroups = TotalSymmGroups;
01664 
01665     return;
01666 
01667 } /* end of cuddZddSymmSummary */
